  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/13a7d3f7ff5a2ec68cef2e287d9d890a.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/13a7d3f7ff5a2ec68cef2e287d9d890a.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT'S THE GAME?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a third person disc golf simulator designed to give an authentic playing experience similar to being on the course with physics of actual disc golf - giving both challenge and reward!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT'S DISC GOLF?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Disc golf plays very similar to golf but uses concaved discs that are thrown into baskets rather than golf balls that are hit by clubs into holes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/6d7d41989d0fb1083c1f12261fbe37e4.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/6d7d41989d0fb1083c1f12261fbe37e4.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=457 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/0242548428afabfe482137ea85a00537.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/0242548428afabfe482137ea85a00537.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT CAN YOU DO?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on courses throughout the world, find lost discs or buy new ones, and learn new throws and styles! Experience realistic gameplay while being surrounded by highly detailed nature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/55b1638a2a80d39654c0e439b0eaf739.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/55b1638a2a80d39654c0e439b0eaf739.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/c0e5f57e5bfca1fc8996c3d1d17e380e.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/c0e5f57e5bfca1fc8996c3d1d17e380e.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/746055faa80c09527a4ae5d3907dc530.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/746055faa80c09527a4ae5d3907dc530.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/d12dea9de4cdd9e6c8c3562e0eb21133.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/d12dea9de4cdd9e6c8c3562e0eb21133.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/381082a835a67049fd02c359f05c2f03.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/381082a835a67049fd02c359f05c2f03.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT COURSES ARE THERE?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are courses constantly added to the game - some of which are actual courses throughout the world. As FLEX continues to grow in popularity, so too will the course list!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/b03383bda84945a4a00db6d57ff1820b.avif?t=1736222836\" width=800 height=538 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/800c70ff2cc9362bddf05bb19ee172b2.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/800c70ff2cc9362bddf05bb19ee172b2.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/6b99ac49791565a548543a4ad618287f.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/6b99ac49791565a548543a4ad618287f.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/d05a9403fecc85e8c3e6963f76cfd209.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/d05a9403fecc85e8c3e6963f76cfd209.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT ELSE IS COMING?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's lots in the works for FLEX, primarily multiplayer! Playing with friends truly multiplies the excitement of disc golf. We want your friends to see that Ace you got just as much as you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/80b98512b6d10e1fb6da45984e12a303.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/80b98512b6d10e1fb6da45984e12a303.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/c29d3cf93408c2285424cc6942369f04.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/c29d3cf93408c2285424cc6942369f04.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/cb47c3baaa818303463c8c3b16fd2b18.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/cb47c3baaa818303463c8c3b16fd2b18.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras/4d1ddde428e0f2e214ce2a5557c82cfc.avif?t=1736222836\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613960/extras_big/4d1ddde428e0f2e214ce2a5557c82cfc.avif?t=1736222836 width=800 height=137 /></span></p>",
